          <div class="wrap">
            <div class="title-wrap">
              <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Bad Breath and Product Questions</h2>
              <div class="section-description">
                <p>Use our FAQs below to learn about bad breath, oral health, our zinc ion technology, and which SmartMouth™ product is right for you. Don’t see the answer to your question? Reach out to us directly through our Contact Us page.</p>
